OL,3,CMore than 7,000 hate crimes logged in
OL,4,CScotland in first week of new law
OL,6,FScottish police received more than
OL,7,F7,000 online reports of hate crimes
OL,8,Fafter
OL,10,FFrom the 7,152 complaints, Police
OL,11,FScotland recorded 240 as hate crimes `
OL,12,F3.3% of all reports ` while 30 were
OL,13,Flogged as non-crime hate incidents,
OL,14,Fmeaning they did not meet the
OL,15,Fthreshold for a criminal offence.
OL,17,FPolice said the vast majority of
OL,18,Fcomplaints were made anonymously.
