OL,3,CMore than 7,000 hate crimes logged in
OL,4,CScotland in first week of new law
OL,6,FOfficers also dealt with 430 incidents
OL,7,Fin the first week where a hate crime
OL,8,Ftag was added for those submitting
OL,9,Fonline reports.
OL,11,FMeanwhile there were 34 calls to
OL,12,Feither 101 or 999 relating to a hate
OL,13,Fcrime and 141 emails sent to Police
OL,14,FScotland for the same purpose.
OL,16,FNearly half of all the complaints made
OL,17,Fonline were made on the first day, the
OL,18,Ffigures showed, before the number of
OL,19,Freports slowed later in the week.
