OL,6,FSome 120 of the crimes reported had a
OL,7,Fracial aggravator attached, the
OL,8,Ffigures showed, while 42 had an
OL,9,Faggravator for sexual orientation, 38
OL,10,Ffor disability, 21 for both age and
OL,11,Freligion and eight for transgender
OL,12,Fidentity.
