OL,3,CMore than 7,000 hate crimes logged in
OL,4,CScotland in first week of new law
OL,6,FJustice Secretary Angela Constance has
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is important when we look at
OL,8,Fthe number of hate crimes recorded `
OL,9,F240 ` by Police Scotland in one week
OL,10,Falone, I think that demonstrates that
OL,11,Fthis legislation is required and
OL,12,Fneeded to protect marginalised and
OL,13,Fvulnerable communities most at risk of
OL,14,Fracial hatred and prejudice."
OL,16,FAsked if she thought the legislation
OL,17,Fwas an example of good law, the
OL,18,Fjustice secretary said it was the
OL,19,Fproduct of "some really good cross-
OL,20,Fparty collaboration" and was backed by
OL,21,F82 of Holyrood's 129 MSPs.
