OL,6,FRohini Sharma Joshi, diversity and
OL,7,Finclusions manager at Age Scotland,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's knowing that there's
OL,9,Fsomething there to safeguard you. We
OL,10,Falso need to build confidence for
OL,11,Fcommunities to know they can report it
OL,12,Fand don't have to accept this
OL,13,Fbehaviour.
OL,15,F"We need to understand what we can do
OL,16,Fto ensure this hate is eradicated in
OL,17,FScotland."
